name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Wage arrears within the Shenyang system
On August 12, a person in the Shenbei New District system in Shenyang said that he was unable to pay wages at the grassroots level. It was confirmed by a large number of people in the local system, and even staff from two offices (party committee office and government office) said that they had not been paid.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On August 13, in Rizhao, Shandong, a man robbed a gold shop with an axe and left calmly after the robbery. According to the police report: no one was injured at the scene, the suspect (male, 44 years old) was arrested and the stolen goods involved in the case have been recovered.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On August 12, a netizen exposed that a female police officer from an intelligence brigade in Sichuan used public power to open a box and threaten others. According to the pictures exposed by the netizen, the netizen named "cc is a cat cc" tagged a netizen on Weibo and said "I'm already looking for your jurisdiction" and also showed her police ID.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On August 13, the central bank released the latest financial data, showing that people's deposits increased by 10.66 trillion yuan in the first seven months, and M1 has been negative for four consecutive months.
